  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Help Fund a Skills Center for Orphans in Zambia</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project will build a vocational skills training centre for orphans and vulnerable children in Solwezi District of Zambia. This will help provide free education and vocational skills to 200 children orphaned and vulnerable due to HIV and AIDS who hail from the poorest sections of society in Solwezi District. Education has an enormous impact on the child&apos;s chances for success in life. The center will offer carpentry, joinery, bricklaying, IT skills, tailoring, and other skills.</narrative>
  </description>
